---
title: Fiery Pork Fajitas with Blistered Peppers and Guacamole
description: Fajitas are a guaranteed crowd pleaser—especially when guacamole is involved. If you don’t want your fajitas on the fiery side, simply cut back on the Thai chili pepper!
